value.0: Most of these sheets of paper contain short, hastily scribbled notes. Some appear to be instructions or orders, others requests for said orders, or supply requisitions.

Each line of every filled page in this ledger seems to list a ship name, a date, and a rough listing of cargo. 

Most of the older entries have been crossed out.
Small models of seafaring vessels sit at various points on the map - some at sea, some nearer the shore, presumably docked.
Throw off the rope and row out of the cavern...
